name: MySQL5
queryCode:
select t1.create_man, t1.DURATION,  t1.CREATE_TIME, t1.TYPE_ID, t1.DESCRIPTION,
t1.PRINCIPAL_ID, t2.TITLE as PRINCIPAL_TITLE, t2.IDENTIFIER as PRINCIPAL_IDENTIFIER, 
t2.PROJECT_ID as PILOT_ID, t3.IDENTIFIER as PILOT_IDENTIFIER, t3.NAME as PILOT_NAME
from workload t1, work_item t2, project t3
where t1.PRINCIPAL_ID = t2.ID and t2.PROJECT_ID = t3.ID
